definitions.definition: A person, especially a large male, who is clumsy or a simpleton .
examples: Ouch! You dropped that box on my feet, you lumbering oaf !

definitions.definition: An elf 's child ; a changeling left by fairies or goblins, hence, a deformed or foolish child.

main_definition: ( derogatory ) A person, especially a large male, who is clumsy or a simpleton .
secondary_definitions: ( obsolete ) An elf 's child ; a changeling left by fairies or goblins, hence, a deformed or foolish child.
